dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Mare Island quadrangle, Contra Costa, Solano, Marin, & Sonoma Counties, California
dc_description_s: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch. Relief shown by contours and spot heights; depths shown by contours. "The field work for this map was completed as Open File Report OF-81-234 while Tom Dibblee was with the U.S. Geological Survey. Where appropriate this map has recently been updated and revised by Tom." "Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle MARE ISLAND, CA 1959, DMA 1560 III SE - Series V895, PHOTOREVISED 1980." "First printing, February 2005." Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology. Includes "pertinent references."
dc_publisher_s: Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History
